  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Locke\" title=\"House Locke\"><img alt=\"House Locke 2.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/8/8b/House_Locke_2.svg/50px-House_Locke_2.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/8/8b/House_Locke_2.svg/75px-House_Locke_2.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/8/8b/House_Locke_2.svg/100px-House_Locke_2.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> Lord</span><br />Ondrew Locke</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Locke\" title=\"House Locke\"><img alt=\"House Locke 2.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/8/8b/House_Locke_2.svg/50px-House_Locke_2.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/8/8b/House_Locke_2.svg/75px-House_Locke_2.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/8/8b/House_Locke_2.svg/100px-House_Locke_2.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:Jonelle_Cerwyn_Ondrew_Locke_and_Arnolf_Karstark_by_Amuelia.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Jonelle Cerwyn Ondrew Locke and Arnolf Karstark by Amuelia.jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/2/2e/Jonelle_Cerwyn_Ondrew_Locke_and_Arnolf_Karstark_by_Amuelia.jpg/300px-Jonelle_Cerwyn_Ondrew_Locke_and_Arnolf_Karstark_by_Amuelia.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"338\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/2/2e/Jonelle_Cerwyn_Ondrew_Locke_and_Arnolf_Karstark_by_Amuelia.jpg/450px-Jonelle_Cerwyn_Ondrew_Locke_and_Arnolf_Karstark_by_Amuelia.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/2/2e/Jonelle_Cerwyn_Ondrew_Locke_and_Arnolf_Karstark_by_Amuelia.jpg/600px-Jonelle_Cerwyn_Ondrew_Locke_and_Arnolf_Karstark_by_Amuelia.jpg 2x\" /></a><div><a href=\"/index.php/Jonelle_Cerwyn\" title=\"Jonelle Cerwyn\">Jonelle Cerwyn</a>, Ondrew Locke, and <a href=\"/index.php/Arnolf_Karstark\" title=\"Arnolf Karstark\">Arnolf Karstark</a> by Amuelia</div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<hr /></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Alias</th><td>\nOld Lord Locke<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd37.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd37.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_Oldcastle\" title=\"Lord of Oldcastle\">Lord of Oldcastle</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Racokappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racokappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Locke\" title=\"House Locke\">House Locke</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Northmen\" title=\"Northmen\">Northmen</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Books</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i> <small>(mentioned)</small></li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i> <small>(appendix)</small></li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i> <small>(appendix)</small></li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i> <small>(appears)</small></li></ul></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Ondrew Locke</b> is the Lord of <a href=\"/index.php/Oldcastle\" title=\"Oldcastle\">Oldcastle</a> and the head of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Locke\" title=\"House Locke\">House Locke</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwdappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwdappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Appearance_and_Character\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Appearance and Character</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#A_Clash_of_Kings\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Clash of Kings</i></span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Appearance_and_Character\">Appearance and Character</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Ondrew_Locke&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Appearance and Character\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Ondrew is an old man, with vulturous features<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd37.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd37.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> and no teeth left in his mouth.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd51.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd51.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> Despite his age, he is outspoken and bold.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd46.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd46.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Ondrew_Locke&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Clash_of_Kings\"><i>A Clash of Kings</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Ondrew_Locke&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Clash of Kings\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Ondrew is invited to the <a href=\"/index.php/Harvest_feast\" title=\"Harvest feast\">harvest feast</a> at <a href=\"/index.php/Winterfell\" title=\"Winterfell\">Winterfell</a> but considers himself too old to make the trip.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok16.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok16.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Ondrew_Locke&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Dance with Dragons\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Ondrew, called \"old Lord Locke\", attends <a href=\"/index.php/Wedding_of_Ramsay_Bolton_and_Arya_Stark\" title=\"Wedding of Ramsay Bolton and Arya Stark\">the wedding</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Ramsay_Bolton\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Ramsay Bolton\">Ramsay Bolton</a> and \"<a href=\"/index.php/Arya_Stark\" title=\"Arya Stark\">Arya Stark</a>\" (actually <a href=\"/index.php/Jeyne_Poole\" title=\"Jeyne Poole\">Jeyne Poole</a>) at Winterfell. <a href=\"/index.php/Theon_Greyjoy\" title=\"Theon Greyjoy\">Theon Greyjoy</a> notes that the face of Lord Locke seems bestial in the shifting light, reminding Theon of a vulture.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd37.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd37.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Lord Locke is concerned about the endless snowfall affecting Winterfell. He is overheard saying that <a href=\"/index.php/Old_gods\" title=\"Old gods\">the gods</a> have turned against them all, cursing them with \"a wind as cold as hell itself and snows that never end.\"<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd46.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd46.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Lord Locke is last seen having breakfast, sitting beside Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Wyman_Manderly\" title=\"Wyman Manderly\">Wyman Manderly</a>. While Wyman eats sausages and boiled eggs, the \"toothless\" Locke contents himself with gruel. When Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Hosteen_Frey\" title=\"Hosteen Frey\">Hosteen Frey</a> attacks Wyman with a <a href=\"/index.php/Longsword\" title=\"Longsword\">longsword</a>, Lord Locke starts shouting for a <a href=\"/index.php/Maester\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Maester\">maester</a> to tend to the wounded man.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd51.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd51.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Ondrew_Locke&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\" style=\"-webkit-column-width:200px; -moz-column-width:200px; column-width:200px; -webkit-column-count:2; -moz-column-count:2; column-count:2;\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd37.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd37.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd37.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd37.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\">1.2</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_37\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 37\">Chapter 37</a>, The Prince of Winterfell.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Racokappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racokappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings-Appendix\" title=\"A Clash of Kings-Appendix\">Appendix</a>.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwdappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwdappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Appendix\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Appendix\">Appendix</a>.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd51.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd51.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\">4.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd51.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-1\">4.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_51\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 51\">Chapter 51</a>, Theon I.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd46.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd46.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\">5.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd46.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-1\">5.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_46\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 46\">Chapter 46</a>, A Ghost in Winterfell.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Racok16.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok16.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings-Chapter_16\" title=\"A Clash of Kings-Chapter 16\">Chapter 16</a>, Bran II.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 202604031